{"tid":962570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[寫手夾硬整到個紀錄啦] C朗成意甲單季入球最多葡人","createTime":"2018-12-31T03:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T03:44:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"020c28efb2b13323888cf515c8811171471e10c5","tid":962570,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"2018-12-30 12:10:35<br />\n<br />\n　　1力克森多利亞，19戰得53分，創下意甲半程最高得分成績。此外，C朗在今年最後一戰仍不忘寫下新紀錄，以14球成為意甲史上單季入球最多的葡萄牙球員，可惜今年「埋單」合共只入48球，連續7年總入球達50大關的走勢宣告結束。<br />\n<br />\n　　C朗上仗作客亞特蘭大時首次在意甲擔任後備，球隊便幾乎出事，結果由他後備上陣扳平保住不敗和一分，C朗可說「踢少一陣都不行」，今戰也需回歸正選，僅兩分鐘便為主隊先拔頭籌，這亦是他本季意甲的第13球，超越前輩雷巴路斯在1988年至1989年球季為祖雲攻入12球的紀錄，成為意甲單季入球最多的葡萄牙人。<br />\n<br />\n　　之後球證透過VAR（視頻助理裁判）判主隊的安利簡恩在禁區內犯手球，加利亞雷拿射入12碼，於33分鐘為森多利亞扳平1：1至完半場，這亦是加利亞雷拿連續9場意甲有入球，對上一個獲此成績的是2005年的祖雲射手查斯古特。不過，客軍守將阿歷士費拉利在禁區內被指犯手球，球證透過VAR核實後判<span style=\"color: red;\">祖雲獲12碼，C朗「操刀」</span>中鵠成2：1。之後森多利亞有一記入球，經VAR判決「越位」在先，結果祖雲憑着C朗及VAR而盡取3分。"},{"pid":"7e909cd5bd336dfa87bf6bb93e7d47b53a34e113","tid":962570,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pEd6DRYR6m8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpEd6DRYR6m8&d=LTuk7bByEYVromtWsWAKrACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a3d7cbb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pEd6DRYR6m8</a><br />\n<br />\n朗迷垃撚圾12碼都敢攞出黎j，傷殘人士都入到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5be239338af45460a1181abd5731d74bc81892f","tid":962570,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kTeG6o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kTeG6o.gif&h=5154d75d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dfb4abd3cd64a2b926f5e275e10ea99fcb147a6","tid":962570,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"踢咗半季=其他人一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\nC朗2018年係皇馬入嘅波<br />\n到依家多過bale 1球<br />\n<br />\n而轉咗祖記呢半季<br />\nDybala 踢咗成年<br />\n只係入多阿朗1球"},{"pid":"00385b03288dd5697b81ce8a692b16cc5eed7c79","tid":962570,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5be239338af45460a1181abd5731d74bc81892f","tid":962570,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kTeG6o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kTeG6o.gif&h=5154d75d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"學界水準式插花"},{"pid":"2e01d476923dba5d2b3e36832615daa742b27505","tid":962570,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"屍朗應該踢拉素、熱那亞呢類球隊證明實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc01e73b270053a3572383b199085f024ea98b","tid":962570,"uid":3115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e909cd5bd336dfa87bf6bb93e7d47b53a34e113","tid":962570,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pEd6DRYR6m8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpEd6DRYR6m8&d=LTuk7bByEYVromtWsWAKrACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a3d7cbb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pEd6DRYR6m8</a><br />\n<br />\n朗迷垃撚圾12碼都敢攞出黎j，傷殘人士都入到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"所以12碼唔計,明未"},{"pid":"cce52dd8a7d601e09fca6810069407ce3d91c343","tid":962570,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7e909cd5bd336dfa87bf6bb93e7d47b53a34e113","tid":962570,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pEd6DRYR6m8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpEd6DRYR6m8&d=LTuk7bByEYVr